pages.text:
Events
.entry-header
Sundays: 12:30- 3:00pm
Live Jazz with Linda Cole ($5 cover)
Every Sunday except the last Sunday of the month.
The show starts around 1 pm. Get there early for a good seat.
No reservations required. Limited Menu during the show.
Mondays: 7:00pm
APA Sanctioned 8-Ball League.
Mixed league (men & women)
All experience levels welcome. This is a handicap league so everyone has a chance to win.
Ask for more information at the front desk if you would like to play.
Tuesdays: 7:00pm
BCA Sanctioned 8-Ball League.
Mixed league (men & women)
All experience levels welcome. This is a handicap league so everyone has a chance to win.
Ask for more information at the front desk if you would like to play or contact
larry@flaglerbca.co
Wednesdays: 7:00pm
9-Ball Tournament.
BCA rules apply. $10.00 buy-in
nine ball tournament $10.00 buy-in starts at 730 pm
Thurs-Fri: All day long
Open Play.
Play pool and have fun with friends. All tables available to the public.
Saturday: Noon - 6pm
Kids Play Free
Kids 16 and under play free when accompanied by an adult. All aspiring young pool players welcome.
Saturdays: 12:00pm - 6:00pm
Kid's 16 and under play free.
From 12:00pm until 6:00. With a paying adult.
Every Day:
HAPPY HOUR.
Every day from 3:00pm til 6:00pm.
Domestic Beer $2.50; Wells $3.00.
All Day, every day: Domestic buckets (5 beers): $12.50/bucket!
.entry-content
.entry-footer
